.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, peas, onion, mango, vanmelon
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, skateboard, trike, van
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, house, gospel, jazz, d&b

1. the person eating blueberry is the person who likes red
2. the person eating peas is the fan of dubstep
3. the person driving the airplane is the person who likes green
4. the person eating onion is the person driving the quad-bike
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the old-gold-smoker is the fan of d&b
7. the kools-smoker is the person who likes yellow
8. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle
9. the person eating mango is on the far left
10. the chesterfields-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of house
11. the kools-smoker is to the left or right of the fan of jazz
12. the lucky-strike-smoker is the person driving the trike
13. the person eating vanmelon is the parliaments-smoker
14. the person eating mango is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   mango	|    onion	|     blueberry	|    peas	|    vanmelon	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Transport	|     van	|      quad-bike	|      skateboard	| trike	|     airplane	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Music-Genre		|     house	|     jazz	|     d&b	|     dubstep	|     gospel	|
